name: doubleclickbidmanager
title: DoubleClick Bid Manager API
description: API for viewing and managing your reports in DoubleClick Bid Manager.

parameters.name: prettyPrint
parameters.desc: Returns response with indentations and line breaks.

parameters.name: quotaUser
parameters.desc: Available to use for quota purposes for server-side applications. Can be any arbitrary string assigned to a user, but should not exceed 40 characters. Overrides userIp if both are provided.

parameters.name: userIp
parameters.desc: IP address of the site where the request originates. Use this if you want to enforce per-user limits.

parameters.name: fields
parameters.desc: Selector specifying which fields to include in a partial response.

parameters.name: key
parameters.desc: API key. Your API key identifies your project and provides you with API access, quota, and reports. Required unless you provide an OAuth 2.0 token.

parameters.name: oauth_token
parameters.desc: OAuth 2.0 token for the current user.

fields.name: reports
fields.desc: Retrieved reports.

fields.name: kind
fields.desc: Identifies what kind of resource this is. Value: the fixed string "doubleclickbidmanager#listReportsResponse".

fields.name: reportDataStartTimeMs
fields.desc: The starting time for the data that is shown in the report. Note, reportDataStartTimeMs is required if metadata.dataRange is CUSTOM_DATES and ignored otherwise.

fields.name: schedule
fields.desc: Information on how often and when to run a query.

fields.name: timezoneCode
fields.desc: Canonical timezone code for report data time. Defaults to America/New_York.

fields.desc: Query ID.

fields.name: reportDataEndTimeMs
fields.desc: The ending time for the data that is shown in the report. Note, reportDataEndTimeMs is required if metadata.dataRange is CUSTOM_DATES and ignored otherwise.

schemas.name: QuerySchedule
schemas.desc: Information on how frequently and when to run a query.

fields.name: nextRunMinuteOfDay
fields.desc: Time of day at which a new report will be generated, represented as minutes past midnight. Range is 0 to 1439. Only applies to scheduled reports.

fields.name: nextRunTimezoneCode
fields.desc: Canonical timezone code for report generation time. Defaults to America/New_York.

fields.name: endTimeMs
fields.desc: Datetime to periodically run the query until.

fields.name: frequency
fields.desc: How often the query is run.

fields.name: status
fields.desc: Report status.

fields.name: googleCloudStoragePath
fields.desc: The path to the location in Google Cloud Storage where the report is stored.

fields.name: reportDataEndTimeMs
fields.desc: The ending time for the data that is shown in the report.

fields.name: reportDataStartTimeMs
fields.desc: The starting time for the data that is shown in the report.

schemas.name: DownloadLineItemsRequest
schemas.desc: Request to fetch stored line items.

fields.name: filterIds
fields.desc: Ids of the specified filter type used to filter line items to fetch. If omitted, all the line items will be returned.

fields.name: filterType
fields.desc: Filter type used to filter line items to fetch.

fields.name: format
fields.desc: Format in which the line items will be returned. Default to CSV.

fields.name: fileSpec
fields.desc: File specification (column names, types, order) in which the line items will be returned. Default to EWF.

schemas.name: FilterPair
schemas.desc: Filter used to match traffic data in your report.

fields.name: type
fields.desc: Filter type.

fields.name: value
fields.desc: Filter value.

schemas.name: RowStatus
schemas.desc: Represents the upload status of a row in the request.

fields.desc: Row number.

fields.name: changed
fields.desc: Whether the stored entity is changed as a result of upload.

fields.name: entityId
fields.desc: Entity Id.

fields.name: entityName
fields.desc: Entity name.

fields.name: errors
fields.desc: Reasons why the entity can't be uploaded.

fields.name: dryRun
fields.desc: Set to true to get upload status without actually persisting the line items.

fields.name: format
fields.desc: Format the line items are in. Default to CSV.

fields.name: lineItems
fields.desc: Line items in CSV to upload. Refer to  Entity Write File Format for more information on file format.

fields.name: errors
fields.desc: Reasons why upload can't be completed.

fields.name: rowStatus
fields.desc: Per-row upload status.

fields.name: lineItems
fields.desc: Retrieved line items in CSV format. Refer to  Entity Write File Format or  Structured Data File Format for more information on file formats.

fields.name: format

schemas.name: RunQueryRequest
schemas.desc: Request to run a stored query to generate a report.

fields.name: reportDataEndTimeMs
fields.desc: The ending time for the data that is shown in the report. Note, reportDataEndTimeMs is required if dataRange is CUSTOM_DATES and ignored otherwise.

fields.name: reportDataStartTimeMs
fields.desc: The starting time for the data that is shown in the report. Note, reportDataStartTimeMs is required if dataRange is CUSTOM_DATES and ignored otherwise.

fields.name: timezoneCode
fields.desc: Canonical timezone code for report data time. Defaults to America/New_York.

fields.name: uploadStatus

schemas.desc: Key used to identify a report.

fields.name: queryId
fields.desc: Query ID.

fields.desc: Report ID.

schemas.name: DownloadRequest
schemas.desc: Request to fetch stored insertion orders, line items, TrueView ad groups and ads.

fields.name: fileTypes
fields.desc: File types that will be returned.

fields.name: filterIds
fields.desc: The IDs of the specified filter type. This is used to filter entities to fetch. At least one ID must be specified. Only one ID is allowed for the ADVERTISER_ID filter type. For INSERTION_ORDER_ID or LINE_ITEM_ID filter types, all IDs must be from the same Advertiser.

fields.name: filterType
fields.desc: Filter type used to filter line items to fetch.

fields.name: version
fields.desc: SDF Version (column names, types, order) in which the entities will be returned. Default to 3.

fields.name: adGroups
fields.desc: Retrieved ad groups in SDF format.

fields.name: ads
fields.desc: Retrieved ads in SDF format.

fields.name: insertionOrders
fields.desc: Retrieved insertion orders in SDF format.

fields.name: lineItems
fields.desc: Retrieved line items in SDF format.

fields.name: kind
fields.desc: Identifies what kind of resource this is. Value: the fixed string "doubleclickbidmanager#listQueriesResponse".

fields.name: queries
fields.desc: Retrieved queries.

schemas.name: Parameters
schemas.desc: Parameters of a query or report.

fields.name: filters
fields.desc: Filters used to match traffic data in your report.

fields.name: groupBys
fields.desc: Data is grouped by the filters listed in this field.

fields.name: includeInviteData
fields.desc: Whether to include data from Invite Media.

fields.name: metrics
fields.desc: Metrics to include as columns in your report.

fields.name: type
fields.desc: Report type.

fields.name: format
fields.desc: Format of the generated report.

fields.name: googleDrivePathForLatestReport
fields.desc: The path in Google Drive for the latest report.

fields.name: latestReportRunTimeMs
fields.desc: The time when the latest report started to run.

fields.name: locale
fields.desc:
Locale of the generated reports. Valid values are cs CZECH de GERMAN en ENGLISH es SPANISH fr FRENCH it ITALIAN ja JAPANESE ko KOREAN pl POLISH pt-BR BRAZILIAN_PORTUGUESE ru RUSSIAN tr TURKISH uk UKRAINIAN zh-CN CHINA_CHINESE zh-TW TAIWAN_CHINESE

An locale string not in the list above will generate reports in English.

fields.name: sendNotification
fields.desc: Whether to send an email notification when a report is ready. Default to false.

fields.name: dataRange
fields.desc: Range of report data.

fields.name: reportCount
fields.desc: Number of reports that have been generated for the query.

fields.name: running
fields.desc: Whether the latest report is currently running.

fields.name: shareEmailAddress
fields.desc: List of email addresses which are sent email notifications when the report is finished. Separate from sendNotification.

fields.name: title
fields.desc: Query title. It is used to name the reports generated from this query.

fields.name: googleCloudStoragePathForLatestReport
fields.desc: The path to the location in Google Cloud Storage where the latest report is stored.

methods.name: runquery
methods.desc: Runs a stored query to generate a report.

methods.name: deletequery
methods.desc: Deletes a stored query as well as the associated stored reports.

pathParams.name: queryId
pathParams.desc: Query ID with which the reports are associated.

methods.name: downloadlineitems
methods.desc: Retrieves line items in CSV format.

methods.desc: Uploads line items in CSV format.
